msgstr "<big id=\"layer7-most-conn\">0</big> ເຮັດໃຫ້ມີການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຫຼາຍທີ່ສຸດ"

#: applications/luci-app-nlbwmon/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/nlbw/display.js:893
