msgstr "<big id=\"layer7-most-rx\">0</big> ເຮັດໃຫ້ມີການດາວໂຫຼດຫຼາຍທີ່ສຸດ"

#: applications/luci-app-nlbwmon/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/nlbw/display.js:894
